Czech Stocks Gain for Second Day as NWR, Erste Group Bank Rally

-- B y   K r y s t o f   C h a m o n i k o l a s
-- 
2011-08-23T07:35:33Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-23/czech-stocks-gain-for-second-day-as-nwr-erste-group-bank-rally.html
The Czech Republic’s equity index
rose for a second day as coal company New World Resources Plc
and  Austria ’s  Erste Group Bank AG (EBS)  gained more than 1.7 percent.  The PX gauge of 14 companies added 0.8 percent to 1,007.4,
after advancing 1.1 percent yesterday.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Krystof Chamonikolas in Prague at 
